      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[bb(sf(R))** = {x in bb(sf(R)) &#x2223; x != 0}]\n\nOther restrictions can be indicated in an obvious way, as shown below.\n\nstem:[bb(sf(R))_(>0) = {x in bb(sf(R)) &#x2223; x > 0}]\n\nThe symbols stem:[rm(&#8739;R)] and stem:[RR] are also used.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
